org.pac4j.play

Class CallbackController

  • java.lang.Object
    • play.mvc.Results
      • play.mvc.Controller
        • org.pac4j.play.CallbackController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    play.mvc.Http.HeaderNames, play.mvc.Http.Status
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SecurityCallbackController

    public class CallbackController
extends play.mvc.Controller

    This controller handles the callback from the identity provider to finish the authentication process.

    The default url after login (if none has originally be requested) can be defined via the setDefaultUrl(String) method.

    Since:
    1.5.0
    Author:
    Jerome Leleu, Michael Remond
